ations.jpg\" alt=\"La-Gatta-Navigation-Destinations\"  class=\"\"></picture></div><div class=\"text\"><span class=\"h2\">Destinations</span></div></a><a href=\"https://lagatta.com/experiences/\"><div class=\"image\"><picture class=\"\"><source type=\"image/jpg\" srcset=\"\" sizes=\"\"><img src=\"https://lagatta.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/La-Gatta-Navigation-Experiences.jpg\" alt=\"La-Gatta-Navigation-Experiences\"  class=\"\"></picture></div><div class=\"text\"><span class=\"h2\">Experiences</span></div></a><a href=\"https://lagatta.com/dining/\"><div class=\"image\"><picture class=\"\"><source type=\"image/jpg\" srcset=\"\" sizes=\"\"><img src=\"https://lagatta.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/La-Gatta-Navigation-Dining.jpg\" alt=\"La-Gatta-Navigation-Dining\"  class=\"\"></picture></div><div class=\"text\"><span class=\"h2\">Dining</span></div></a>    </nav>\n    <nav class=\"secondary\">\n      <a href=\"#\" class=\"openBook\"><span class=\"h3\">Contact</span></a><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/lagattaluxuryyacht/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"h3\">Instagram</span></a>    </nav>\n  </div>\n</header>\n<div class=\"splash\">\n  <div class=\"background media\">\n    <div class=\"desktop\">\n      <video class=\"desktop\" playsinline muted loop poster=\"\"><source src=\"https://lagatta.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/la-gatta-opening-v3.mov\" type=\"video/mp4\" /></video>    </div>\n    <div class=\"mobile\">\n      <video class=\"mobile\" playsinline muted loop poster=\"https://lagatta.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/La-Gatta-Homepage-Hero-Mobile.jpg\"><source src=\"https://lagatta.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/la-gatta-opening-v3.mov\" type=\"video/mp4\" /></video>    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"text\">\n    <h1 class=\"h1\">Create unforgettable memories</h1>\n    <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 187 21\"><path d=\"M0 .3493077h3.55130181v17.0544331H14.177883v3.2468032H0V.3493077Zm116.225931 0h16.402155v3.30688797h-6.410657V20.650544h-3.580841V3.65619567h-6.410657V.3493077Zm26.537728 0h16.401417v3.30688797h-6.409918V20.650544h-3.580841V3.65619567h-6.410658V.3493077ZM32.6602349.20243382h3.2913601L44.8464651 20.650544H30.1937446l3.2337595-3.2468032H39.71853L34.2479444 4.46771103 27.4052824 20.650544H23.766841L32.6602349.20243382Zm64.5927055 0h3.2920986l8.894133 20.44811018H94.7864513l3.2337594-3.2468032h6.2910263L98.8413897 4.46771103 91.9987278 20.650544h-3.6391802L97.2529404.20243382Zm77.5608296 0h3.292099L187 20.650544h-14.652719l3.233759-3.2468032h6.291025l-5.469847-12.93602977-6.843401 16.18283297h-3.63844L174.81377.20243382ZM68.2637142 12.4130696l3.0897578-3.10363835h7.2968218v8.52832925C76.6579011 19.5505476 73.798546 21 70.2177053 21c-6.3235173 0-10.4818409-4.524161-10.4818409-10.4428823V10.5c0-5.68431652 4.3318643-10.5 10.4242402-10.5 3.5217628 0 5.6876961.9865772 7.7664887 2.7542564l-2.4915974 2.50353238c-1.479156-1.21727305-2.9819417-1.97983041-5.4196305-1.97983041-3.7241038 0-6.5539211 3.27795825-6.5539211 7.16566583V10.5c0 4.1762628 2.7426776 7.2502296 6.872201 7.2502296 1.9059904 0 3.6384414-.6090074 4.8798094-1.5347581v-3.8024019h-6.9497405Z\" fill=\"#FFF\" fill-rule=\"nonzero\"/></svg>  </div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"main home\">\n\n  <section class=\"hero center\">\n    <div class=\"media\" data-observe=\"fadeIn\">\n      <div class=\"desktop\">\n        <video class=\"desktop\" playsinline muted loop poster=\"https://lagatta.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/lagatta-poster.jpg\"><source src=\"https://lagatta.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/1_LAGATA_20-second_h265.mov\" type=\"video/mp4\" /></video>      </div>\n      <div class=\"mobile\">\n        <video class=\"mobile\" playsinline muted loop poster=\"https://lagatta.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/lagatta-poster.jpg\"><source src=\"https://lagatta.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/1_LAGATA_20-second_h265.mov\" type=\"video/mp4\" /></video>      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"intro center\">\n    <div class=\"text\">\n      <h1 class=\"h2\" data-observe=\"fadeIn\">Come Onboard</h1>\n      <div class=\"p\" data-observe=\"fadeIn\">\n        <p>Enjoy superior comfort paired with stunning scenery and once in a life time experiences. Let’s go away for a while.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"images\">\n      <div class=\"image\" data-observe=\"fadeIn\">\n        <picture class=\"\"><source type=\"image/jpg\" srcset=\"\" sizes=\"\"><img src=\"https://lagatta.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/La-Gatta-Homepage-Beach-Walk.jpg\" alt=\"La-Gatta-Homepage-Beach-Walk\"  class=\"\"></picture>      </div>\n      <div class=\"image\" data-observe=\"fadeIn\">\n        <picture class=\"\"><source type=\"image/jpg\" srcset=\"\" sizes=\"\"><img src=\"https://lagatta.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/La-Gatta-Homepage-Sailing.jpg\" alt=\"La-Gatta-Homepage-Sailing\"  class=\"\"></picture>      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"quote\" data-observe=\"fadeIn\">\n      <p class=\"h2\">Disconnect and move at the speed of the wind</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"image\" data-observe=\"fadeIn\">\n      <div class=\"desktop\">\n        <picture class=\"\"><source type=\"image/jpg\" srcset=\"\" sizes=\"\"><img src=\"https://lagatta.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/La-Gatta-Homepage-Private-Beach-Platform-Desktop-1-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"La-Gatta-Homepage-Private-Beach-Platform-Desktop\"  class=\"\"></picture>      </div>\n      <div class=\"mobile\">\n        <picture class=\"\"><source type=\"image/jpg\" srcset=\"\" sizes=\"\"><img src=\"https://lagatta.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/La-Gatta-Homepage-Private-Beach-Platform-Mobile.jpg\" alt=\"La-Gatta-Homepage-Private-Beach-Platform-Mobile\"  class=\"\"></picture>      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"experiences center\">\n    <div class=\"header\">\n      <h2 class=\"h2\" data-observe=\"fadeIn\">Experiences</h2>\n      <div class=\"p\" data-observe=\"fadeIn\">\n        <p>The activities onboard La Gatta are plentiful and fun whether in the water, onboard the deck or on land.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"carousel\" data-observe=\"fadeIn\">\n      <div class=\"slides\">\n        <div class=\"slide\"><a href=\"https://lagatta.com/experiences/\"><div class=\"image\"><picture class=\"\"><source type=\"image/jpg\" srcset=\"\" sizes=\"\"><img src=\"https://lagatta.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/La-Gatta-Homepage-Snorkeling.jpg\" alt=\"La-Gatta-Homepage-Snorkeling\"  class=\"\"></picture></div><div class=\"text\"><h2 class=\"h3\">Scuba, Snorkel + More</h2><p class=\"p\">With a full gamut of snorkeling gear on board, we can assist you in locating reefs to explore!</p><span class=\"link\">Learn More</span></div></a></div><div class=\"slide\"><a href=\"https://lagatta.com/experiences/\"><div class=\"image\"><picture class=\"\"><source type=\"image/jpg\" srcset=\"\" sizes=\"\"><img src=\"https://lagatta.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/La-Gatta-Homepage-Electric-Hydrofoil-Surfboard.jpg\" alt=\"La-Gatta-Homepage-Electric-Hydrofoil-Surfboard\"  class=\"\"></picture></div><div class=\"text\"><h2 class=\"h3\">Lift E-Foil</h2><p class=\"p\">Nothing could be more fun than an electric hydrofoil surfboard!</p><span class=\"link\">Learn More</span></div></a></div><div class=\"slide\"><a href=\"https://lagatta.com/experiences/\"><div class=\"image\"><picture class=\"\"><source type=\"image/jpg\" srcset=\"\" sizes=\"\"><img src=\"https://lagatta.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/La-Gatta-Homepage-Boating.jpg\" alt=\"La-Gatta-Homepage-Boating\"  class=\"\"></picture></div><div class=\"text\"><h2 class=\"h3\">Towable Toys</h2><p class=\"p\">Take Gatto Veloce out for an afternoon of wakeboarding or for sunset cocktails.</p><span class=\"link\">Learn More</span></div></a></div><div class=\"slide\"><a href=\"https://lagatta.com/experiences/\"><div class=\"image\"><picture class=\"\"><source type=\"image/jpg\" srcset=\"\" sizes=\"\"><img src=\"https://lagatta.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/La-Gatta-Homepage-Jacuzzi-1.jpg\" alt=\"La-Gatta-Homepage-Jacuzzi\"  class=\"\"></picture></div><div class=\"text\"><h2 class=\"h3\">Jacuzzi</h2><p class=\"p\">Imagine yourself in the Jacuzzi, watching a spectacular sunset with your favorite drink in hand.</p><span class=\"link\">Learn More</span></div></a></div>      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"more\">\n    <div class=\"columns center\">\n      <div class=\"column\"><a href=\"https://lagatta.com/onboard/\"><div class=\"image\" data-observe=\"fadeIn\"><picture class=\"\"><source type=\"image/jpg\" srcset=\"\" sizes=\"\"><img src=\"https://lagatta.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/La-Gatta-Homepage-Layout-Amenities.jpg\" alt=\"La-Gatta-Homepage-Layout-Amenities\"  class=\"\"></picture></div><div class=\"text\" data-observe=\"fadeIn\"><h2 class=\"h3\">Layout & Amenities</h2><p class=\"p\">From the flybridge to the skirts and from the bow towards the stern; spaces are plentiful and all are connected simultaneously.</p><span class=\"link\">Learn More</span></div></a></div><div class=\"column\"><a href=\"https://lagatta.com/dining/\"><div class=\"image\" data-observe=\"fadeIn\"><picture class=\"\"><source type=\"image/jpg\" srcset=\"\" sizes=\"\"><img src=\"https://lagatta.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/La-Gatta-Homepage-Dining.jpg\" alt=\"La-Gatta-Homepage-Dining\"  class=\"\"></picture></div><div class=\"text\" data-observe=\"fadeIn\"><h2 class=\"h3\">Dining Onboard</h2><p class=\"p\">Whether it be light, restorative afternoon snacks or exquisite dinners alfresco, each dish is prepared with skillfulness and love.</p><span class=\"link\">Learn More</span></div></a></div><div class=\"column\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"openCrew\"><div class=\"image\" data-observe=\"fadeIn\"><picture class=\"\"><source type=\"image/jpg\" srcset=\"\" sizes=\"\"><img src=\"https://lagatta.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/La-Gatta-Crew-Captain-Driving.jpg\" alt=\"La-Gatta-Crew-Captain-Driving\"  class=\"\"></picture></div><div class=\"text\" data-observe=\"fadeIn\"><h2 class=\"h3\">The Crew</h2><p class=\"p\">Our crew has over ten years of experience chartering both sailing and motor yachts. They look forward to adventuring with you!</p><span class=\"link\">Learn More</span></div></a></div>    </div>\n  </section>\n\n</div>\n\n    \n<footer class=\"center\">\n  <div class=\"instagram\">\n    <div class=\"images\">\n      <div class=\"image\">\n        <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CFNCetFBoxj/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n          <picture class=\"\"><source type=\"image/jpg\" srcset=\"https://lagatta.com/wp-content/themes/la-gatta/assets/images/jpg/instagram2.jpg\" sizes=\"1px\"><img src=\"https://lagatta.com/wp-content/themes/la-gatta/assets/images/jpg/instagram2.jpg\" alt=\"La Gatta\"  class=\"\"></picture>        </a>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"image\">\n        <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CFNCBS9BAui/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n          <picture class=\"\"><source type=\"image/jpg\" srcset=\"https://lagatta.com/wp-content/themes/la-gatta/assets/images/jpg/instagram3.jpg\" sizes=\"1px\"><img src=\"https://lagatta.com/wp-content/themes/la-gatta/assets/images/jpg/instagram3.jpg\" alt=\"La Gatta\"  class=\"\"></picture>        </a>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"image\">\n        <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CFKFb_Sh32d/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n          <picture class=\"\"><source type=\"image/jpg\" srcset=\"https://lagatta.com/wp-content/themes/la-gatta/assets/images/jpg/instagram4.jpg\" sizes=\"1px\"><img src=\"https://lagatta.com/wp-content/themes/la-gatta/assets/images/jpg/instagram4.jpg\" alt=\"La Gatta\"  class=\"\"></picture>        </a>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"image\">\n        <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CFKEzn1BW0o/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n          <picture class=\"\"><source type=\"image/jpg\" srcset=\"https://lagatta.com/wp-content/themes/la-gatta/assets/images/jpg/instagram1.jpg\" sizes=\"1px\"><img src=\"https://lagatta.com/wp-content/themes/la-gatta/assets/images/jpg/instagram1.jpg\" alt=\"La Gatta\"  class=\"\"></picture>        </a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"text\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/lagattaluxuryyacht/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" class=\"footerlink\">Join our journey on <span>Instagram</span></a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"logo\">\n    <div class=\"menu button\">\n      <a href=\"#\" class=\"openMenu\">\n        <i class=\"icon-menu\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 14 14.4\" xml:space=\"preserve\"><g transform=\"rotate(45 4.86424237 18.57174863)\"><path d=\"M-1.8.2 3 8.8l-4.5 9.1-4.2-8.6L-1.8.2z\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#fff\"/><circle cx=\"-1.3\" cy=\"8.9\" r=\"1.5\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" fill=\"#fff\"/></g></svg></i>\n        <span>Menu</span>\n      </a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"image\">\n      <a href=\"/\">\n        <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 187 21\"><path d=\"M0 .3493077h3.55130181v17.0544331H14.177883v3.2468032H0V.3493077Zm116.225931 0h16.402155v3.30688797h-6.410657V20.650544h-3.580841V3.65619567h-6.410657V.3493077Zm26.537728 0h16.401417v3.30688797h-6.409918V20.650544h-3.580841V3.65619567h-6.410658V.3493077ZM32.6602349.20243382h3.2913601L44.8464651 20.650544H30.1937446l3.2337595-3.2468032H39.71853L34.2479444 4.46771103 27.4052824 20.650544H23.766841L32.6602349.20243382Zm64.5927055 0h3.2920986l8.894133 20.44811018H94.7864513l3.2337594-3.2468032h6.2910263L98.8413897 4.46771103 91.9987278 20.650544h-3.6391802L97.2529404.20243382Zm77.5608296 0h3.292099L187 20.650544h-14.652719l3.233759-3.2468032h6.291025l-5.469847-12.93602977-6.843401 16.18283297h-3.63844L174.81377.20243382ZM68.2637142 12.4130696l3.0897578-3.10363835h7.2968218v8.52832925C76.6579011 19.5505476 73.798546 21 70.2177053 21c-6.3235173 0-10.4818409-4.524161-10.4818409-10.4428823V10.5c0-5.68431652 4.3318643-10.5 10.4242402-10.5 3.5217628 0 5.6876961.9865772 7.7664887 2.7542564l-2.4915974 2.50353238c-1.479156-1.21727305-2.9819417-1.97983041-5.4196305-1.97983041-3.7241038 0-6.5539211 3.27795825-6.5539211 7.16566583V10.5c0 4.1762628 2.7426776 7.2502296 6.872201 7.2502296 1.9059904 0 3.6384414-.6090074 4.8798094-1.5347581v-3.8024019h-6.9497405Z\" fill=\"#FFF\" fill-rule=\"nonzero\"/></svg>      </a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"book button\">\n      <a href=\"#\" class=\"openBook\">\n        <i class=\"icon-book\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 12.9 15.7\" xml:space=\"preserve\"><path d=\"M12.2 11.6c-.3-.2-.7-.1-.9.2C9.9 14.1 7.1 15 4.7 14l4.1-7.1 1.7 1c.3.2.8.1 1-.3s.1-.8-.3-1l-1.7-1 .6-1.1c1 .2 2-.2 2.5-1.1.6-1.1.3-2.5-.9-3.2-1.1-.6-2.5-.3-3.2.9-.5 1-.3 2 .3 2.8l-.6 1L6.5 4l-.1-.1c-.3-.2-.8-.1-1 .3s0 .8.3 1h.1l1.7 1-4.1 7.1C1.3 11.7.6 8.8 1.9 6.4c.2-.3.1-.7-.2-.9-.3-.2-.7-.1-.9.2-1.8 3.2-.6 7.2 2.5 9s7.2.8 9.1-2.3c.2-.3.1-.6-.2-.8zM9.6 1.8c.3-.5 1-.7 1.5-.4.5.3.7 1 .4 1.5-.3.5-1 .7-1.5.4-.5-.3-.7-1-.4-1.5z\" fill=\"#fff\"/></svg></i>\n        <span>Book</span>\n      </a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"navigation primary\">\n    <ul>\n      <li><a href=\"https://lagatta.com/onboard/\" class=\"footerlink\">Onboard</a></li><li><a href=\"https://lagatta.com/destinations/\" class=\"footerlink\">Destinations</a></li><li><a href=\"https://lagatta.com/experiences/\" class=\"footerlink\">Experiences</a></li><li><a href=\"https://lagatta.com/dining/\" class=\"footerlink\">Dining</a></li>    </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"navigation secondary\">\n    <ul>\n            <li class=\"copyright\">&copy; La Gatta 2026</li>\n      <li><a href=\"https://thebeauxartsdigital.com\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Site By</a></li>\n    </ul>\n  </div>\n</footer>  </div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"modal\">\n  <div class=\"modal-book\">\n<div class=\"bar\">\n  <h3 class=\"h3\">Book</h3>\n  <a href=\"#\" class=\"closeModal closeBook\" aria-label=\"Close modal\"><span></span></a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"book center\">\n  <div class=\"form\">\n    <div class=\"text\">\n      <h2 class=\"h2\"><p>Come explore the world aboard La Gatta, a brand new seventy-seven foot luxury catamaran.</p>\n</h2>\n    </div>\n    <form autocomplete=\"on\">\n      <div class=\"columns\">\n        <div class=\"column\">\n          <div class=\"row\">\n            <label for=\"book-name\" class=\"h3\">Name</label>\n            <input type=\"text\" class=\"p input\" id=\"book-name\" name=\"book-name\" placeholder=\"Name Lastname\" autocomplete=\"name\" required />\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"row\">\n            <label for=\"book-email\" class=\"h3\">Email Address</label>\n            <input type=\"email\" class=\"p input\" id=\"book-email\" name=\"book-email\" placeholder=\"name@email.com\" autocomplete=\"email\" required />\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"row\">\n            <label for=\"book-phone\" class=\"h3\">Phone Number</label>\n            <input type=\"tel\" class=\"p input\" id=\"book-phone\" name=\"book-phone\" placeholder=\"000 000 0000\" autocomplete=\"tel\" required />\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"column\">\n          <div class=\"row\">\n            <label for=\"book-location\" class=\"h3\">Where do you live?</label>\n            <input type=\"text\" class=\"p input\" id=\"book-location\" name=\"book-location\" placeholder=\"City, State\" autocomplete=\"address-level2\" required />\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"row\">\n            <label for=\"book-destinations\" class=\"p input\">Select destination(s)</label>\n            <div class=\"dropdown input\">\n              <input type=\"text\" class=\"h3\" id=\"book-destinations\" name=\"book-destinations\" placeholder=\"Destinations\" autocomplete=\"off\" required />\n              <i class=\"icon-chevron\"><?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<svg width=\"16px\" height=\"11px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 11\" version=\"1.1\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\">\n    <title>Group 2</title>\n    <g id=\"Page-1\" stroke=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" stroke-linecap=\"square\">\n        <g id=\"TBA-La-Gatta-15\" transform=\"translate(-822.000000, -509.000000)\" stroke=\"#FFFFFF\" stroke-width=\"1.5\">\n            <g id=\"Group-2\" transform=\"translate(830.000000, 514.500000) rotate(-270.000000) translate(-830.000000, -514.500000) translate(826.500000, 508.500000)\">\n                <polyline id=\"Line-2\" points=\"-3.94093228e-13 -3.48054918e-14 7 6 -4.26325641e-14 12\"></polyline>\n            </g>\n        </g>\n    </g>\n</svg></i>\n              <ul class=\"options\">\n                <li class=\"p\" data-value=\"St. Maarten\r\">St. Maarten\r</li><li class=\"p\" data-value=\"Turks & Caicos\r\">Turks & Caicos\r</li><li class=\"p\" data-value=\"Bahamas\">Bahamas</li>              </ul>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"row\">\n            <label for=\"book-size\" class=\"h3\">Size of Company</label>\n            <input type=\"number\" class=\"p input\" id=\"book-size\" name=\"book-size\" placeholder=\"Size of Company\" autocomplete=\"off\" required />\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"submit\">\n        <button type=\"submit\">Submit</button>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"success\"><p class=\"p\">Hello everybody</p></div>\n    </form>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"questions\">\n    <h2 class=\"h2\">For enquiries please contact your preferred charter broker.</h2>\n    <a href=\"mailto:\" class=\"h3\"></a>\n  </div>\n</div></div>\n  <div class=\"modal-crew\">\n<div class=\"bar\">\n  <h3 class=\"h3\">The Crew</h3>\n  <a href=\"#\" class=\"closeModal closeCrew\" aria-label=\"Close modal\"><span></span></a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"crew center\">\n  <div class=\"columns\">\n    <div class=\"bio\"><div class=\"wrap\"><div class=\"image\"><picture class=\"\"><source type=\"image/jpg\" srcset=\"\" sizes=\"\"><img src=\"https://lagatta.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/La-Gatta-Crew-Jason-Van-Groeningen-2025.jpg\" alt=\"La-Gatta-Crew-Jason-Van-Groeningen-2025\"  class=\"\"></picture></div><div class=\"text\"><h2 class=\"h3\">Captain Jason Van Groeningen</h2><div class=\"p\"><p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\">Capt. Jason has extensive navigational experience in the Caribbean and Mediterranean, with over 200+ charters during his time as a charter captain. He holds a Yachtmaster’s, over 45,000 nautical miles and 3 trans &#8211; Atlantic crossings; you can rest assured that you are in good hands. He grew up on the west coast of South Africa and is an avid sailor, surfer and free diver, with a love for fishing. He has a diverse set of interests, having studied at the Campus for Performing Arts prior to embarking on his yachting career, and plays classical piano and guitar. Jason is friendly, flexible and goes above and beyond to make your time aboard memorable.</p>\n</div></div></div></div><div class=\"bio\"><div class=\"wrap\"><div class=\"image\"><picture class=\"\"><source type=\"image/jpg\" srcset=\"\" sizes=\"\"><img src=\"https://lagatta.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/La-Gatta-Crew-Chef-Nataliia-Blyxniuk-2025.jpg\" alt=\"La-Gatta-Crew-Chef-Nataliia-Blyxniuk-2025\"  class=\"\"></picture></div><div class=\"text\"><h2 class=\"h3\">Chef Nataliia Blyxniuk</h2><div class=\"p\"><p class=\"m_2169818823560564276p1\">Nataliia is from Ukraine and has always had a deep passion for both cooking and the sea, which ultimately led her to pursue a career as a chef aboard yachts. <u></u><u></u>Given her desire to travel and experience the world while crafting exquisite food menus and fine <u></u><u></u>dining presentations, it was only natural for her to enter the yachting industry in 2018.<u></u><u></u></p>\n<p class=\"m_2169818823560564276p1\">Nataliia’s main interests include developing new recipes, exploring, trekking, reading, contemporary theatre as well as traveling and discovering local cultures, traditions, and cuisine. <u></u><u></u>She is committed to using only the freshest, locally sourced ingredients of the highest quality. <u></u><u></u>Nataliia will design a bespoke and exciting menu plan tailored to your preferences.</p>\n</div></div></div></div><div class=\"bio\"><div class=\"wrap\"><div class=\"image\"><picture class=\"\"><source type=\"image/jpg\" srcset=\"\" sizes=\"\"><img src=\"https://lagatta.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/La-Gatta-Crew-Arturo-Lemus-2025.jpg\" alt=\"La-Gatta-Crew-Arturo-Lemus-2025\"  class=\"\"></picture></div><div class=\"text\"><h2 class=\"h3\">Mate Arturo Lemus</h2><div class=\"p\"><p>Arturo&#8217;s journey from his Mexican roots to a life at sea has been an adventure. While leading a land-based life, on top of his personal trainer certifications he obtained his Masters degree in human nutrition and pursued his career as a health professional. Embracing the challenges outside of the familiar, he decided to go off to work on cruise ships, where he discovered his passion for travel and maritime life. He became a dive instructor and afterwards he obtained his captain license and led day charters in the Cayman Islands.</p>\n<p>Later, he joined some of the most prestigious superyachts in the world to widen his experience. Through his adventures, he has evolved into an exceptional seaman and travelled far and wide, from Thailand, Bahamas, Seychelles and the Maldives to remote corners of Russia&#8217;s eastern coast. Onboard La Gatta, Arturo will ensure that every experience is both enjoyable and safe. When in need, reach out to him, he will be ready to make your adventure unforgettable.</p>\n</div></div></div></div><div class=\"bio\"><div class=\"wrap\"><div class=\"image\"><picture class=\"\"><source type=\"image/jpg\" srcset=\"\" sizes=\"\"><img src=\"https://lagatta.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/La-Gatta-Crew-Sara-Fernandez-2025.jpg\" alt=\"La-Gatta-Crew-Sara-Fernandez-2025\"  class=\"\"></picture></div><div class=\"text\"><h2 class=\"h3\">Stewardess Sara Fernandez</h2><div class=\"p\"><p>Sara was born and raised in Barcelona, Spain. Her dreamy nature got herself out of her surroundings and traveling solo for a year. This experience evolved into a transformative chapter, leading her to discover her true calling at sea as it was always meant to be. She initially became a dive instructor, with over 2,000 dives in places like Thailand, Seychelles, Maldives, Bahamas, Cayman Islands, and even braved the chilly waters of Russia.</p>\n<p>As she always thrives out of her comfort zone, she achieved her captain license of 200 tons and worked on superyachts for over 4 years. She learnt all about organizing day-to-day duties and catering to guest requests, accommodating all needs, personalized service and care for their stay. Her newly found passion is cocktail making, so she will have you sipping on a refreshing adult drink in no time. Sara’s goal is to help provide the environment that ensures her guest to have an incredible holiday.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n</div></div></div></div>  </div>\n</div></div>\n  <div class=\"modal-gallery\"></div>\n</div>\n<script type=\"speculationrules\">\n{\"prefetch\":[{\"source\":\"document\",\"where\":{\"and\":[{\"href_matches\":\"/*\"},{\"not\":{\"href_matches\":[\"/wp-*.php\",\"/wp-admin/*\",\"/wp-content/uploads/*\",\"/wp-content/*\",\"/wp-content/plugins/*\",\"/wp-content/themes/la-gatta/*\",\"/*\\\\?(.+)\"]}},{\"not\":{\"selector_matches\":\"a[rel~=\\\"nofollow\\\"]\"}},{\"not\":{\"selector_matches\":\".no-prefetch, .no-prefetch a\"}}]},\"eagerness\":\"conservative\"}]}\n</script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" id=\"main-js-js-extra\">\n/* <![CDATA[ */\nvar LAGATTA = {\"ajaxurl\":\"https://lagatta.com/wp-admin/admin-ajax.php\",\"themedir\":\"https://lagatta.com/wp-content/themes/la-gatta\",\"security\":\"337370d0cd\"};\n//# sourceURL=main-js-js-extra\n/* ]]> */\n</script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"https://lagatta.com/wp-content/themes/la-gatta/assets/scripts/app.bundle.js?ver=1705933426\" id=\"main-js-js\"></script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n", "fetch_error": "", "checked_at": "2026-03-16T14:33:13.765999+00:00"}